INSERT INTO peers(torrent_id, peer_id, ip, port, user_id, real_uploaded, real_downloaded)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
        ON CONFLICT (torrent_id, peer_id, ip, port) DO UPDATE
        SET
            last_seen_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
            real_uploaded = $6,
            real_downloaded = $7
